                      d="M13.01 14h.005"></path><path d="M16.015 14h.005"
                    ></path><path d="M13.015 17h.005"></path><path
                      d="M7.01 17h.005"></path><path d="M10.01 17h.005"
                    ></path></svg
                  ></span
                >
                Fecha: 15/08/2024
              </p>

              <p class="flex">
                <span>
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-clock-hour-7"
                    ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"
                    ></path><path d="M12 12m-9 0a9 9 0 1 0 18 0a9 9 0 1 0 -18 0"
                    ></path><path d="M12 12l-2 3"></path><path d="M12 7v5"
                    ></path></svg
