              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="flex">
              <span
                ><svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="24"
                  height="24"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-map-pin"
                  ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"
                  ></path><path d="M9 11a3 3 0 1 0 6 0a3 3 0 0 0 -6 0"
                  ></path><path
                    d="M17.657 16.657l-4.243 4.243a2 2 0 0 1 -2.827 0l-4.244 -4.243a8 8 0 1 1 11.314 0z"
                  ></path></svg
                ></span
              >
              Ubicación: Apolo Urban Kitchen TRC
            </p>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-5 flex">
            <span>
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-microphone"
                ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                  d="M9 2m0 3a3 3 0 0 1 3 -3h0a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v5a3 3 0 0 1 -3 3h0a3 3 0 0 1 -3 -3z"
                ></path><path d="M5 10a7 7 0 0 0 14 0"></path><path
                  d="M8 21l8 0"></path><path d="M12 17l0 4"></path></svg
              ></span
            >
            Platicas:
          </h3>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">
                OpenAI en .NET <span class="text-green-600 font-normal"
                  >Fabrizio Arriola</span
                >
              </p>
              <div class="flex space-x-4">
                <span>
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-brand-openai"
                    ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"
                    ></path><path
                      d="M11.217 19.384a3.501 3.501 0 0 0 6.783 -1.217v-5.167l-6 -3.35"
                    ></path><path
                      d="M5.214 15.014a3.501 3.501 0 0 0 4.446 5.266l4.34 -2.534v-6.946"
                    ></path><path
                      d="M6 7.63c-1.391 -.236 -2.787 .395 -3.534 1.689a3.474 3.474 0 0 0 1.271 4.745l4.263 2.514l6 -3.348"
                    ></path><path
                      d="M12.783 4.616a3.501 3.501 0 0 0 -6.783 1.217v5.067l6 3.45"
                    ></path><path
                      d="M18.786 8.986a3.501 3.501 0 0 0 -4.446 -5.266l-4.34 2.534v6.946"
                    ></path><path
                      d="M18 16.302c1.391 .236 2.787 -.395 3.534 -1.689a3.474 3.474 0 0 0 -1.271 -4.745l-4.308 -2.514l-5.955 3.42"
                    ></path></svg
                  >
                </span>

                <span>
                  <svg
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    width="24"
                    height="24"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-brand-c-sharp"
                    ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"
                    ></path><path
                      d="M10 9a3 3 0 0 0 -3 -3h-.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 -3.5 3.5v5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 3.5 3.5h.5a3 3 0 0 0 3 -3"
                    ></path><path d="M16 7l-1 10"></path><path d="M20 7l-1 10"
                    ></path><path d="M14 10h7.5"></path><path d="M21 14h-7.5"
                    ></path></svg
                  >
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold">
                GIT - Buenas practicas y consejos avanzados <span
                  class="text-green-600 font-normal"
                  >Leonardo Salazar - @SCLEO97
                </span>
                <div class="flex space-x-4">
                  <span>
                    <svg
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                      width="24"
                      height="24"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-brand-git"
                      ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"
                      ></path><path d="M16 12m-1 0a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0"
                      ></path><path d="M12 8m-1 0a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0"
                      ></path><path d="M12 16m-1 0a1 1 0 1 0 2 0a1 1 0 1 0 -2 0"
                      ></path><path d="M12 15v-6"></path><path d="M15 11l-2 -2"
                      ></path><path d="M11 7l-1.9 -1.9"></path><path
                        d="M13.446 2.6l7.955 7.954a2.045 2.045 0 0 1 0 2.892l-7.955 7.955a2.045 2.045 0 0 1 -2.892 0l-7.955 -7.955a2.045 2.045 0 0 1 0 -2.892l7.955 -7.955a2.045 2.045 0 0 1 2.892 0z"
                      ></path></svg
                    >
                  </span>
                </div>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl mt-5 flex space-x-2">
            <span>
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="24"
                height="24"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-ticket"
                ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                  d="M15 5l0 2"></path><path d="M15 11l0 2"></path><path
                  d="M15 17l0 2"></path><path
                  d="M5 5h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3a2 2 0 0 0 0 4v3a2 2 0 0 1 -2 2h-14a2 2 0 0 1 -2 -2v-3a2 2 0 0 0 0 -4v-3a2 2 0 0 1 2 -2"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </span>
            Boleto:

            <a
              href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/dev-meetup-0824-tickets-982998443807?aff=oddtdtcreator"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-green-600"
            >
              Da click para conseguir tu boleto
            </a>
          </h3>

          <div>
            <p class="text-justify">
              Encuentra tu boleto a este evento <b>gratuito</b> y ven a compartir
              un buen momento con mas personas como tu. Recuerda, invita a tus amigos,
              compañeros de trabajo, familia.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-1">
          <Image
            src={localFlayerSM}
            alt="Flayer de evento TRC JS"
            class="my-auto rounded-r-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </Card>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-4">
    <Card title="Únete a nuestra comunidad de programadores">
      <p class="text-justify">
        ¿Eres apasionado por la programación y quieres conectar con otros
        desarrolladores que compartan tus intereses? ¡Entonces, únete a nuestra
        comunidad de programadores en WhatsApp! <b>En nuestro grupo, podrás:</b>
      </p>

      <ul class="list-disc ml-5">
        <li>Conectar con otros programadores de México y del mundo</li>
        <li class="text-green-600">Compartir conocimientos y experiencias</li>
        <li>Obtener ayuda y soporte en tus proyectos</li>
        <li class="text-green-600">
          Participar en discusiones y debates sobre las últimas tendencias en
          programación
        </li>
        <li>Acceder a recursos y herramientas exclusivas para programadores</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-center">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">¡No esperes más!</span> Únete a nuestra
        comunidad hoy mismo y comienza a conectar con otros programadores que comparten
        tus pasiones!
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/Lrdy2KsIrza8Qc2iR96E3S"
        target="_blank"
        class="px-4 mt-4 py-3 w-auto text-center text-2xl flex text-green-600 border border-green-600 hover:bg-green-600 hover:text-zinc-800 border-spacing-1 rounded-full transition ease-in-out hover:ease-in hover:animate-pulse hover:-translate-y-1"
      >
        <span>
          <svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            width="30"
            height="30"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-brand-whatsapp"
            ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
              d="M3 21l1.65 -3.8a9 9 0 1 1 3.4 2.9l-5.05 .9"></path><path
              d="M9 10a.5 .5 0 0 0 1 0v-1a.5 .5 0 0 0 -1 0v1a5 5 0 0 0 5 5h1a.5 .5 0 0 0 0 -1h-1a.5 .5 0 0 0 0 1"
            ></path></svg
          >
        </span>
        WhatsApp
      </a>
    </Card>
  </div>
</Layout>
